EDIT: https link fixed

For the time being, https links on typophile need to be written with the syntax \<a href="https:www link"\> text \</a\> else they come out broken; so, here it is: [history](http://web.archive.org/web/20140828181309/https:/www.typotheque.com/fonts/history).
